# AI Agent Development Guide

Solana token airdrop campaign page. Static React SPA — visitors connect a wallet, check eligibility, claim tokens.

## Constraints

**MUST:** static-hostable (no SSR/server deps), preserve wallet connect + eligibility + claim flow, use `--campaign-*` CSS vars for theming, keep ErrorBoundary in App.tsx, validate with `pnpm build`.

**MUST NOT:** touch `.bonkit/` (recipient data), add server dependencies, use `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`, expose private keys, bypass wallet connection.

## Editing Priority

1. `src/layout-config.ts` — labels, visibility, options (typed as `LayoutConfig`)
2. `src/theme.ts` — colors, fonts, radius (typed as `ThemeTokens`)
3. `.env` — `VITE_RPC_URL`, `VITE_SITE_URL`
4. `src/App.tsx` — layout switch, providers (keep ErrorBoundary)
5. `src/layouts/` — layout components (maintain `config, colors, slots` prop interface)
6. `public/` — image assets
7. `src/components/ui/` — UI primitives (last resort)

**Avoid** `campaign.config.json` — Zod-schema validated, invalid edits break app + studio.

## File Map

```
src/main.tsx                    # React DOM entry
src/App.tsx                     # Error boundary + wallet provider + theme vars + layout
src/styles.css                  # Tailwind entry (imports styles/campaign.css)
src/theme.ts                    # Theme tokens
src/layout-config.ts            # Layout config (labels, images, addresses, options)
src/types.ts                    # LayoutConfig + ThemeTokens types
src/layouts/                    # centered, two-column, hero-banner, step-card
src/layouts/slots.tsx           # SlotProps type (changes break all layouts)
src/layouts/wallet-slots.tsx    # Wallet-aware slots (connect, claim, eligibility)
src/layouts/shared/             # HeroBackground, FooterBlock, CountdownBlock, StatusBadge, TokenIdentity
src/components/wallet/          # Solana wallet adapter
src/components/ui/              # shadcn-style primitives
src/hooks/use-airdrop.ts        # Airdrop state machine
src/lib/airdrop-client.ts       # Airdrop SDK wrapper
```

## Layout Switch

```tsx
// In App.tsx, change import:
import { TwoColumnLayout } from "./layouts/two-column"
// Available: CenteredLayout, TwoColumnLayout, HeroBannerLayout, StepCardLayout
```

## OG Image (not included by default)

1. `public/og-image.png` (1200x630)
2. Add to `index.html`: `<meta property="og:image" content="%VITE_SITE_URL%/og-image.png" />`
3. Change `twitter:card` to `"summary_large_image"`
4. Set `VITE_SITE_URL` in `.env`

## Stack

TailwindCSS v4, Radix UI, class-variance-authority, lucide-react, Solana wallet adapter, @tanstack/react-query
